sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#555555;line-height:1.7;">
    Last issue we fixed noisy search. This issue tackles the next problem: ge=
tting an agent to <em>reason</em> through a multi-step process instead of try=
ing to do everything in a single prompt.
  </p>
  <p style=3D"margin:0;font-family:'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Geneva,Verdana,sans-seri=
f;font-size:15px;color:#555555;line-height:1.7;">
    <strong>This issue's patterns:</strong> How to chain prompts so each step=
 improves the next, and how to define those steps in YAML playbooks that anyo=
ne on the customer's team can modify without touching code.
  </p>
</td></tr>

<!-- AGENT SPOTLIGHT -->
